Once upon a time, there was a Monkey, she resided in a jamun tree. There lived  a crocodile and his wife in the river
  crocodile used to see monkey and wonder how sweet the fruit of this tree will be, so one day monkey gave
  some fruits to him,
    he bacame happy
    and then wife saw the fruits and wondered how sweet the monkey will beso crocodile went and brought the monkey with him.
    monkey got to know thetruth and jumped back.
